reviewText: Generally I love "wet"-themed soft-core, and  I love explicit soft-core, and  this title is both (more explicit than most Peach titles). But still,  something is lacking. The women aren't the hottest (not enough all-naturals) and the vignettes are paced a little poorly where the timing of everything feels a little bit off.  There has to be some build-up and anticipation to these things.

This is another Peach compilation DVD, masquerading as a"theme" - they basically take a lot of water-themed scenes and put them together, so this one may have scenes you have already seen (if you're a Peach fan). However, I liked it and it really "worked" for me.

Rachel Elizabeth is an astonishingly hot brunette. Teanna Kai is a busty, gorgeous Asian babe who always puts on a nice show, and Mason Marconni is a sexy-latte-skinned stunner. But the babe that really floated my boat in this title was Jessica Jaymes. She's a lithe, busty brunette beauty w/ gorgeous jugs and, most importantly, a penchant for spreading to "show all". All the babes in this one share their pink treasures, but Jessica's sexy privates are on display here, close-up and in vivid, living color. Wow, those legs are hot, especially when they are far apart.

Overall, sexy title, especially if you're into jacuzzis, beaches, swimming pools, etc...and babes drenched and looking hot.

I wasn't sure what to expect with a title like "Wet". However, I wasn't dissapointed. The scenes were entertaining. The women were hot. I have 2 Peach DVDs. Both are first rate. I would buy their stuff again.

I'm really not into the "naked woman on the beach rub sand all over her body thing" unless she is really hot. Teanna Kai was good. The other woman I could have done without. But I still would give this a "4". It is still superior. There is something about a naked wet woman caressing herself that is sexy. The scene with the girl in the bathtub is outstanding. not a 5. But then again what is?
